name: Alphabet Animals
description:
This print is from original cut-paper illustrations featuring an animal for every letter of the alphabet. 

Size: 11"x17" print with a minimum of 1/2" border all around– a standard ready made frame size.
Paper: high-quality, 13 pt. recycled matte paper.
Edition Size: 100 / Individually numbered and signed by artist.

-Frame not included.
-Prints are wrapped for protection and shipped in tubes.

name: Animal of Your Choice
description:
Commission to have an animal of your choice created just for you. Here are some ideas: a portrait of your pet, your zodiac animal or that animal you love seeing on Discovery Channel.

The size of the artwork will vary depending on the animal, but it will fit and be loosely mounted within a 6"x8" archival drawing paper. 

Once your payment has been made, please email [hello@christina-song.com] attaching a reference photo of your animal. Upon purchase, allow a full 1-2 weeks for the artwork to be completed. You'll be notified by email once it's ready for shipping.

Note: The right image is just an example. Artwork is packaged inside plastic sleeves for protection and shipped flat.

name: Object of Your Choice
description:
Commission to have an object of your choice created just for you. Some examples include your trusty bicycle, your grandfather's watch, your favorite childhood toy, or maybe even your favorite pair of shoes. Makes for a great gift for him or her.

The size of the artwork will vary depending on the object, but it will fit and be loosely mounted within a 6"x8" archival drawing paper. 

Once your payment has been made, please email [hello@christina-song.com] attaching a reference photo of your object. Upon purchase, allow a full 1-2 weeks for the artwork to be completed. You'll be notified by email once it's ready for shipping.

Note: The right image is just an example. Artwork is packaged inside plastic sleeves for protection and shipped flat.
